			<speak chara="_Miguel">……음. 혹시 내가 알면 안되는 거라면——</speak>
			<show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8" />
			<show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" />
			<speak chara="_Bianka">할아버지는 그냥 계세요!</speak>
			<show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8" />
			<show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right" />
			<speak chara="_Miguel">……!</speak>
			<show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right" opacity="0.8" />
			<show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left" />
			<speak chara="_Bianka">……아녜요.</speak>
			<speak chara="_Bianka">일단, 저희에게 있어 할아버지는 은인이니까요……그러니까, 자신을 제3자라 생각하지 않으셔도 돼요.</speak>
			<show chara="biankaProudClose" position="left" />
			<speak chara="_Bianka">그럼 본론으로 돌아가서——</speak>
			<speak chara="_Bianka">리타, 설명을 부탁해.</speak>
			<show chara="biankaConfidentClose" position="left" />
			<speak chara="_Bianka">우리가 이곳에 온 목적이, 무엇인지.</speak>
			<show chara="biankaConfidentClose" position="left" opacity="0.8" />
			<show chara="rita17SmileClose" position="right" />
			<speak chara="_Rita">……좋아요, 비앙카님.</speak>
			<show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right" />
			<bgm src="11_16_themeOtto.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
			<speak chara="_Rita">우선——여러분들은 「양자의 바다」란 이름을 들어보셨나요?</speak>
			<goto goto="130" clockwise="1" />
